# Backend API base URL
# Jangan sertakan /api — path endpoint sudah memuat prefix /api di client
#
# Backend Go (go-rag-edu) default:
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:8080
#
# Jika memakai backend NestJS (sesuai step.md):
# VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:3000

# Rate limiting FE (in-memory, hooks.server.ts):
# - Global: 200 req/menit per IP
# - /auth/login: 20 req/15 menit per IP
# - /api/*: 60 req/menit per IP
